    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Love Machine</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Casey Morgan letter score Rob Tannenbaum's June 4 article for casting Diane Warren as incomplete woman0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The blurb in your article focuses on Warren's issues in therapy, and the article ends with a quote that seems bent on making Warren look pathetic (''I've got nothing else to do'' on a Friday night than wait for clients). It's a shame that an article on such an interesting and successful woman has to be cast as the tale of an incomplete woman.</p>
        <p>Casey Morgan</p>
        <p>New York</p>
      </block>
